item.title: CVE-2017-8968|2024-08-05T16:55:21.820Z -- hewlett%20packard%20enterprise -- hpe%20restful%20interface%20tool
item.description: A remote execution of arbitrary code vulnerability has been identified in HPE RESTful Interface Tool 1.5, 2.0 (hprest-1.5-79.x86_64.rpm, ilorest-2.0-403.x86_64.rpm). The issue is resolved in iLOREST v2.1 or subsequent versions.
